Systray CD Player: Reproduce tus CDs de audio desde la bandeja del sistema / Play Audio CD from systry
(c) 2012 Alfonso Saavedra "Son Link"
http://sonlinkblog.blogspot.com/p/systray-cd-player.html
Under GPLv3 License

Para instalarlo ejecuta como root el script install.sh
For install execute with root user the install.sh script

Command line parameters:
-d | --device <device>: set the device from read CD (usualy /dev/sr0 or /dev/cdrom)
-f | --force : if running another scdp instance kill her and run nwe instance
